    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak[s]</strong> finely on a clean board</p><p>Carefully cut the parcel[s] open and squeeze your <strong>garlic</strong> out of the skin</p><p>Serve the <strong>sliced steak</strong> with the <strong>roasted potatoes, red onions </strong>and<strong> garlic</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon the<strong> béarnaise sauce</strong> over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
